{"title":"爸爸的老师","authors":["任溶溶"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸的老师（儿童诗）\t任溶溶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的爸爸是数学家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都知道他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们要是还不知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为没有长大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有天早晨爸爸起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像有什么要事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知他跟妈妈说道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要去望望老师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的爸爸还有老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说多么新鲜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这老师是怎么个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我倒很想见见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我起劲地求我爸爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带我去看看他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸对我眼睛一眨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说了一声：“好吧！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是爸爸临走以前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我反复叮咛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我注意这个那个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我当然都答应。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一路想他这老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是怎么个人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一定是胡子很长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满肚子的学问。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他当然是比爸爸强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是位老老专家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要不是老老专家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么教我爸爸？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是结果你猜猜看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸对谁鞠躬？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这事要让同学看到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我都要脸红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞠躬的人如果是我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那还不算稀奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为爸爸这位老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我的老师！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我都念三年级了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她却教一年级。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的爸爸向她鞠躬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说多么有趣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师看着爸爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像看个娃娃："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你这些年非常努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成绩的确很大。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想爸爸怎么回答？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这得谢谢老师！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我全靠着您的指点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道二二得四。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是我才恍然大悟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管什么专家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有一年级的老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经教导过他。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}